        <h2>COLLEGE APPLICATION ESSAY BOOT CAMP</h2>
        <p>Most students would agree that the most painful part of the college application process writing the essay.  Sign up for a Get It Done Boot Camp and we will help you complete a competitive college application essay or personal statement in two short days.</p>
        
        <h2>Pre-Boot Camp:</h2>
        <p>Prior to Boot Camp, you will schedule a 60 minute online video chat with a Fat Envelope Writing Coach in order to determine your most competitive essay hook.</p>
        
