        <ul>
          <li>Overview</li>
          <li> Getting Ready for College:</li>
          <li> Things to look for when choosing a college </li>
          <li> How to prepare for common college trials: roommates, dorm food, Teacher’s Assistants, and the occasional challenges of missing your family</li>
          <li> College success: what it is like to make friends,</li>
          <li> getting involved on campus and how to manage time </li>
          <li> Essay System Step One: Determining your Power Topic</li>
